## Frontend (Vite)
# Local dev (backend running locally):
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000

# Production example (Render backend):
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend.onrender.com

# If deploying ONLY the frontend to Vercel:
# - This repo includes a Vercel serverless proxy at /api/* (api/[...path].js)
# - Set BACKEND_URL in Vercel env vars to your backend base URL (no trailing slash), e.g.
#   BACKEND_URL=https://your-backend.onrender.com
